INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (228, 1, '2011-03-14 10:14:52', '2011-03-14 09:14:52', '<div class="zemanta-img" style="margin: 1em; display: block;">\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignright" width="219" caption="Image via Wikipedia"]<a href="http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Radio_DAB_.JPG"><img title="DAB RADIO 2008" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/Radio_DAB_.JPG/300px-Radio_DAB_.JPG" alt="DAB RADIO 2008" width="219" height="164" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nIf you own a radio, tv or computer (in Germany) the <a class="zem_slink" title="Gebühreneinzugszentrale" rel="wikipedia" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geb%C3%BChreneinzugszentrale">GEZ</a> fuckers come every year to collect a fee for the public radio and television people. I don''t have a problem with paying for public radio and television, despite the fact that I don''t really listen to either (they don''t measure up to <a class="zem_slink" title="NPR" rel="homepage" href="http://www.npr.org">NPR</a> or <a class="zem_slink" title="Public Broadcasting Service" rel="homepage" href="http://www.pbs.org">PBS</a>, and I''ve been spoiled), only have the radio because it came with the stereo system and ripping it out would break the rest of the shit built in, and don''t own a TV. I do have a problem with the inefficiency and waste of the GEZ though. It doesn''t matter that literally every single person in Germany has to pay the fucking GEZ fee because there is NO ONE who doesn''t at least have a radio, the GEZ still feels the need to waste money and time sending people, real life people, around to "check" if you have a radio or TV.\r\n\r\nThis is completely retarded. We all have to pay the fee, so why isn''t it just added into our taxes? We all get paper invoices every two months to pay the fee, and 80% of us forget and end up paying a late fee. What the FUCK!? The GEZ is paying hundreds or thousands of people a salary to wander around annoying the shit out of people, they''re killing tons of trees to print invoices for the 88 million Germans, or however many there are, every two months and WHY!? For what fucking reason is this fee not included in a culture tax!?\r\n\r\nFuck the GEZ and the German government for not being more efficient and considerate. FUCK THEM!\r\n\r\nIt really irritates me that money and resources all over the world are just thrown away like this when they just don''t need to be.\r\n<h6 class="zemanta-related-title" style="font-size: 1em;">Related articles</h6>\r\n<ul class="zemanta-article-ul">\r\n	<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href="http://lifm.wordpress.com/2011/01/07/a-guide-to-german-billing/">A guide to German billing</a> (lifm.wordpress.com)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="zemanta-pixie" style="margin-top: 10px; height: 15px;"><a class="zemanta-pixie-a" title="Enhanced by Zemanta" href="http://www.zemanta.com/"><img class="zemanta-pixie-img" style="border: medium none; float: right;" src="http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=768c2b21-b69b-4f63-93d3-ba2a573dc4a2" alt="Enhanced by Zemanta" /></a></div>', 'GEZ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gez', '', '\nhttp://lifm.wordpress.com/2011/01/07/a-guide-to-german-billing/', '2011-03-14 10:16:16', '2011-03-14 09:16:16', '', 0, 'http://www.zythepsary.com/?p=228', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (203, 1, '2011-03-03 07:48:21', '2011-03-03 07:48:21', 'Seriously, what the fuck should I do for the next few hours. I have tasks, but I don''t want to do any of them. They''re boring me. But I''ve got 3.5 hours to kill until I have to go to the airport and leave this god awful country behind. I''m in <a class="zem_slink" title="Malaysia" rel="geolocation" href="http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=3.13333333333,101.7&amp;spn=10.0,10.0&amp;q=3.13333333333,101.7%20%28Malaysia%29&amp;t=h">Malaysia</a>, I don''t like it. I''ve been in <a class="zem_slink" title="Kuala Lumpur" rel="geolocation" href="http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=3.1475,101.693333333&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=3.1475,101.693333333%20%28Kuala%20Lumpur%29&amp;t=h">Kuala Lumpur</a> for several weeks now, and I don''t mean to be negative, but this country is a shithole. I know what you''re thinking, "Hey, you''ve been in KL, what about the rest of Malaysia?" Well, I''ve been there too, all over the place, and this country is a shithole. White people get beaten up and robbed, which could happen anywhere, but when it happens systematically it''s called a scam. The police treat the victims like it''s their own fault and try to make them sign documents written in <a class="zem_slink" title="Malay language" rel="wikipedia" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malay_language">Malay</a>, and it''s not a second hand story - this fucking happened! Ok, it didn''t happen to me, it happened to my husband, but still. KL is an ugly city that is completely void of any sort of Malay culture, if Malay culture even exists anymore. They''re trying so hard to be Western that they''ve washed away anything that would make the city charming. As we traveled around Malaysia we tried to see the good, and took some pictures of some good stuff. But for me Malaysia gets a "disappointing" rating and is struck from my desired vacation destination list.\r\n\r\nI can''t even rant properly because I''m so dispassionate about the whole thing. Instead of ranting, here''s some images of the non suck in this suck hole.\r\n\r\n[postcasa size=large align=center  showcaptions=yes]http://picasaweb.google.com/data/feed/base/user/lfrankeberger/albumid/5579755520950477153?alt=rss&amp;kind=photo&amp;hl=en_US[/postcasa]', 'Dispassionate about Malaysia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dispassionate-about-malaysia', '', '', '2011-03-23 15:23:21', '2011-03-23 14:23:21', '', 0, 'http://www.zythepsary.com/?p=203', 0, 'post', '', 0);
