arning goals of each event type. Understanding the overarching knowledge types will help us create curriculum that fits into each event type. This will allow us to be more efficient in our content creation, which means we will be able to create more content.\r\n\r\nAs always, comments are welcome and appreciated.\r\n<h4 class="zemanta-related-title">Related articles</h4>\r\n<ul class="zemanta-article-ul">\r\n	<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href="http://www.zythepsary.com/techie/system-thinking/" target="_blank">System Thinking</a> (zythepsary.com)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="zemanta-pixie"><a class="zemanta-pixie-a" title="Enhanced by Zemanta" href="http://www.zemanta.com/"><img class="zemanta-pixie-img" src="http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=311511a3-e259-4c71-b6c4-23e19d21260e" alt="Enhanced by Zemanta" /></a></div>', 'More System Thinking (at a Micro-Level)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1206-revision-2', '', '', '2012-02-07 14:09:38', '2012-02-07 13:09:38', '', 1206, 'http://www.zythepsary.com/rants/1206-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
