Referenced Theory</h4>\r\n<ul class="zemanta-article-ul">\r\n	<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href="http://erinknight.com/post/17966967241/what-is-webmaking" target="_blank">Erin Knight: What is webmaking?</a> (erinknight.com)</li>\r\n	<li class="zemanta-article-ul-li"><a href="http://erinknight.com/post/16589793083/learning-to-make-by-making" target="_blank">Learning to make by making...</a> (erinknight.com)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="zemanta-pixie"><a class="zemanta-pixie-a" title="Enhanced by Zemanta" href="http://www.zemanta.com/"><img class="zemanta-pixie-img" src="http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=2ef37967-365f-42aa-a1b1-dc88696c4f99" alt="Enhanced by Zemanta" /></a></div>', 'Web Literacy Micro-Models', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1246-revision-4', '', '', '2012-02-21 11:51:11', '2012-02-21 10:51:11', '', 1246, 'http://www.zythepsary.com/rants/1246-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
